title: Sedin Alić
text:
Sedin Alić (born 31 May 1989 in Heijlsminde) is a Bosnian-Herzegovinian professional <a href="association%20football">football</a>er.
Club career.
The Danish-born Alić began his career with Christiansfeld IF and joined in July 2006 to the youth side of <a href="S%C3%B8nderjyskE%20Fodbold">SønderjyskE</a>. After one year in the a-youth of <a href="S%C3%B8nderjyskE%20Fodbold">SønderjyskE</a> signed his first professional contract for the club and played until December 2009 only 16 games. On 21 January 2010 signed a two and a half years contract for <a href="Vejle%20Boldklub">Vejle Boldklub</a>.
